with a 116-89 win over the Indiana Pacers.  The Bulls won the Eastern Conference series by four games
to one.   Also tonight, the Orlando Magic avoided elimination with a
101-76 home win against the  Atlanta Hawks . The best-of-seven-
game series resumes April 28 in Atlanta with the Hawks leading
